<item>
  <title>Writefreely.el</title>
  <link>http://127.0.0.1:43110/15Aj7PkCPHfCHqNFUnEMoKBDwqHAJ7b9Q6/n0te.html#org64c77ea</link>
  <author>schizo@autistici.org (Schiz0)</author>
  <guid isPermaLink="false">http://127.0.0.1:43110/15Aj7PkCPHfCHqNFUnEMoKBDwqHAJ7b9Q6/n0te.html#org64c77ea</guid>
  <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2019 10:15:00 +0100</pubDate>

  <description><![CDATA[<p>
  
  </p>

  <p>
  This small library allows you to publish and update your Org-mode files as posts to any instance of the federated blogging platform write freely.
  </p>

  <p>
  <a href="https://github.com/dangom/writefreely.el">https://github.com/dangom/writefreely.el</a>
  </p>

  <p>
  io con la configurazione indicata non son riuscito a farlo funzionare; ho modificato nel seguente modo:
  </p>

  <div class="org-src-container">
  <pre class="src src-emacs-lisp"><span style="color: #5f615c; font-style: italic;">;</span>
  <span style="color: #5f615c; font-style: italic;">;;</span>
  <span style="color: #5f615c; font-style: italic;">;; </span><span style="color: #5f615c; font-style: italic;">writefreely.el</span>
  <span style="color: #5f615c; font-style: italic;">;;</span>
  <span style="color: #5f615c; font-style: italic;">;</span>

  (add-to-list 'load-path <span style="color: #5c3566;">"~/.emacs.d/elpa/writefreely-xxxxxxxx.xxxx/"</span>)

  (<span style="color: #346604;">require</span> '<span style="color: #204a87; font-weight: bold;">writefreely</span>)

  <span style="color: #5f615c; font-style: italic;">;; </span><span style="color: #5f615c; font-style: italic;">(use-package writefreely</span>
  <span style="color: #5f615c; font-style: italic;">;;   </span><span style="color: #5f615c; font-style: italic;">:after org</span>
  <span style="color: #5f615c; font-style: italic;">;;   </span><span style="color: #5f615c; font-style: italic;">:ensure t</span>
  <span style="color: #5f615c; font-style: italic;">;;   </span><span style="color: #5f615c; font-style: italic;">;; Authentification token, if wanted.</span>
  <span style="color: #5f615c; font-style: italic;">;;   </span><span style="color: #5f615c; font-style: italic;">;; Alternatively (setq writefreely-auth-token "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000")</span>
  <span style="color: #5f615c; font-style: italic;">;;   </span><span style="color: #5f615c; font-style: italic;">(setq writefreely-auth-token "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000")</span>

  <span style="color: #5f615c; font-style: italic;">;; </span><span style="color: #5f615c; font-style: italic;">il token che serve per postare nell'istanza dove si ha l'account</span>
  <span style="color: #5f615c; font-style: italic;">;; </span><span style="color: #5f615c; font-style: italic;">lo si ottiene inviando il la riga di comando "curl..."</span>
  <span style="color: #5f615c; font-style: italic;">;; </span><span style="color: #5f615c; font-style: italic;">suggerita qui https://developers.write.as/docs/api/#authenticate-a-user</span>

  (<span style="color: #346604;">setq</span> writefreely-auth-token <span style="color: #5c3566;">"......-....-....-....-........."</span>) 

  <span style="color: #5f615c; font-style: italic;">;;   </span><span style="color: #5f615c; font-style: italic;">:config (load-library "writefreely-auth-token.el.gpg"))</span>
  </pre>
  </div>

  <p>
  e poi, nel gruppo "WriteFreely", ho configurato le variabili
  </p>

  <ul class="org-ul">
  <li>Writefreely Instance Api Endpoint</li>

  <li>Writefreely Instance Url</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
  una cosa che mi sembra decisamente riduttiva √® che i contenuti vengono pubblicati sulle istanze del fediverso solamente nella forma "titolo" + "url" obbligando
  chi legge ad andare sulla piattaforma d'origine
  </p>

  <p>
  anche la mancata generazione di un feed dei messaggi mi sembra un'inutile semplificazione* L‚Äôattivismo per timidi di Introfada √® un manifesto speculativo per una nuova democrazia
